{"tid":2120923,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"放下油門煮晚餐 - 千層麵","createTime":"2020-07-23T03:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T21:14:48.000Z","uid":27669,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3909a8f339c3f54923cb7059cc6b499ab1dafde","tid":2120923,"uid":27669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T03:58:40.000Z","msg":"身為一個外賣仔，但通常都唔會叫外賣<br />\n加上疫情關係就嘗試唔同菜式<br />\n今次想介紹嘅係千層麵<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n芝士碎 大量<br />\n茄汁 小量<br />\n糖 小量<br />\n豬肉碎 十蚊<br />\n蕃茄 三個<br />\n現成千層麵皮 數塊<br />\n<br />\n首先煮個汁，用熱水烚熟啲蕃茄見佢甩哂皮就可以用個獲剷壓爛啲蕃茄，再加啲茄汁同糖，煮到濃稠就可以熄火。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2jvyEZW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2jvyEZW.jpg&h=a5be3d08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住就首先一層醬先，跟住就放千層麵皮，再放醬，再加芝士不停重覆，直到無哂醬為止<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/krfOtTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkrfOtTi.jpg&h=d194631a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要留意啲醬要遮到哂全張麵皮<br />\n<br />\n最後放入焗爐180-190度左右，焗到面頭啲芝士開始溶同燶就完成啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Shgh6He.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FShgh6He.jpg&h=74555ce8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"814abdfe1395e57fad56979edcfe0af631e63075","tid":2120923,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T04:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea98d15b582c3f3b6b7511f0746faa3f2ce3be3b","tid":2120923,"uid":295992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"白汁？"},{"pid":"f6a760a86fb52c1a0cce0ad5607754de5009f900","tid":2120923,"uid":238920,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"只可以講呢個唔係肉醬<br />\n只係蕃茄汁肉碎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb882df0c49a0f9c2abf6bbe40145aa175aad67","tid":2120923,"uid":321352,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你啲材料少到咁，點樣叫肉醬？最低限度都加翻啲月桂葉茄膏洋蔥嗰類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e08d7f45ba0bec1a19da2503702ff82913bbfe7","tid":2120923,"uid":245126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正"},{"pid":"682fbca4b618a215a7a5586246273ef8e864b715","tid":2120923,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:26:38.000Z","msg":"好似爛屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96b39f64d107e43cff94a7e07a70f4462198ed0","tid":2120923,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:58:54.000Z","msg":"好唔好食？"},{"pid":"2331f6a8ff3c9785b134f3c7750870eb86458136","tid":2120923,"uid":27669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d96b39f64d107e43cff94a7e07a70f4462198ed0","tid":2120923,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T19:58:54.000Z","msg":"好唔好食？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"好食"},{"pid":"0a4478825861baebee2a496618c858d3834859ad","tid":2120923,"uid":27669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feb882df0c49a0f9c2abf6bbe40145aa175aad67","tid":2120923,"uid":321352,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你啲材料少到咁，點樣叫肉醬？最低限度都加翻啲月桂葉茄膏洋蔥嗰類<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:47:16.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗加茄膏已經夠味<br />\n同埋屋企無乜調味料食得好清"},{"pid":"26f88c88fff9e98920c2ddb13b85faf8b037db8f","tid":2120923,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T02:48:12.000Z","msg":"自己睇下肉醬點整<br />\n唔好侮辱人地D食物喇"},{"pid":"46815b5